OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAlzheimer's: Adjusting to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbeing your parent's parent 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It's traditionally a disease associated
OL,6, with the elderly. But when their father
OL,7, was diagnosed with early on-set        
OL,8, Alzheimer's aged just 55, two young    
OL,9, brothers made lifestyle changes and    
OL,10, revised career ambitions to help with  
OL,11, his care. So what is it like becoming  
OL,12, your parent's parent?                  
OL,14,FWhen Simon Ruscoe started acting       
OL,15,Fstrangely in 2015, it was initially put
OL,16,Fdown to work stress.                   
OL,18,FThe hands-on, active husband and father
OL,19,Fwas increasingly starting to forget    
OL,20,Fthings and get words muddled. He forgot
OL,21,Fdirections.                            
